<li><a href="/scp-2385">SCP-2385</a> (&quot;Somewhere in the Between&quot;) - Life finds a way. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869528" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;">Shaggydredlocks</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc7"><span>Tales:</span></h4>
<ul>
