<h3 id="toc12"><span>Week of January 15th:</span></h3>
<p>Need a new cybernetic hand? Want some fairy dust in your coffee? Trying to track down an art terrorist? Stop by Three Portlands!</p>
<h4 id="toc13"><span>SCPs:</span></h4>
